Concerns are growing for the whereabouts of Megadeth singer Dave Mustaine's missing mother-in-law who disappeared from a park in San Diego County, California, on Saturday. 

Sally Estabrook, described as a 75-year-old woman with Alzheimer's disease, was last seen at the Pinezanita RV Park & Campgrounds about 4 p.m.

Her husband told deputies he returned from a shower and couldn't find her. Since then search and rescue teams from three counties and a federal agency have been searching for the missing woman.

